						               													<description>The Scafford Gang Enemy Supplement #1&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The Scafford Gang are one of the most dangerous bands of outlaws in the West! Ruthless Mutants lead by Colonel Scafford and his trusty Lieutenants, the Scafford Gang robs trains and towns across the countryside, making their hideouts in the caves and abandoned mines up in the hills. Former Confederates in the Civil War, they despise the law and use their hideous mutations to fill their pockets with gold and Dark Stone.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;This sets adds new large Enemy Record Sheets for 2 of the dangerous Scafford Lieutenants &amp;ndash; Sergeant Bunker and &amp;lsquo;Fast Draw&amp;rsquo; Jeb Scafford, making them full Enemy mini-bosses. It also includes a couple of new outlaw-themed Gear and Artifact cards, as well as a set of new Threat cards that combine various Scafford themed Enemies together, and even Epic Threats to face off against a more dangerous version of each of these Lieutenants with their gang.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;This game supplement enhances the Scafford Gang Deluxe Enemy Pack and Dark Stone Brutes Enemy Pack, as well as the Resin Enemy Figures for Sergeant Bunker and &amp;lsquo;Fast Draw&amp;rsquo; Jeb Scafford.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the publisher&amp;#10;&amp;#10;CONTENTS&amp;#10;&amp;#10;     Sgt. Bunker Enemy Sheet&amp;#10;     'Fast Draw' Jeb Scafford Enemy Sheet&amp;#10;     Card #231 Old Keys (Gear)&amp;#10;     Card #333 Brace of Dark Stone Pistols (Mine Artifact)&amp;#10;     Card #458 Sgt. Bunker and D3+1 Scafford Gang (Low Threat)&amp;#10;     Card #459 Sgt. Bunker, D6 Scafford Gang and 1 Dark Stone Brute (Medium Threat)&amp;#10;     Card #460 Sgt. Bunker, PD Scafford Gang and D3 Dark Stone Brutes (High Threat)&amp;#10;     Card #461 Sgt. Bunker, PD Scafford Gang and D3 Dark Stone Brutes (Epic Threat)&amp;#10;     Card #462 'Fast Draw' Jeb Scafford and D3+1 Scafford Gang (Low Threat)&amp;#10;     Card #463 'Fast Draw' Jeb Scafford, D6 Scafford Gang and 1 Dark Stone Brute (Medium Threat)&amp;#10;     Card #464 'Fast Draw' Jeb Scafford, PD Scafford Gang and D3 Dark Stone Brutes (High Threat)&amp;#10;     Card #465 'Fast Draw' Jeb Scafford, PD Scafford Gang and D3 Dark Stone Brutes (Epic Threat)&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
